org.displaytag.model

Class HeaderCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.displaytag.model.HeaderCell

  • public class HeaderCell
extends Object
    DataObject representing the column header. The header cell contains all the properties common to cells in the same column.
    Version:
    $Revision$ ($Author$)
    Author:
    Fabrizio Giustina
